---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import btnIcon from "../../assets/icons/btn-icon.svg";
---

<section class="lg:py-[112px] py-[48px]">
  <div
    class="max-w-screen-2xl lg:px-20 px-[24px] mx-auto"
  >
  <div class="text-center bg-cardColor rounded-[48px] lg:px-[150px] lg:py-[88px] py-[64px] px-[24px] ">
      <h3
      class="lg:text-[52px] text-center mb-[24px] text-[32px] md:text-[28px] leading-[36px] lg:leading-[56px] font-black  text-textPrimary font-figtree"
    >
  Your onboarding, supported
    </h3>
    <p
      class="text-[16px] text-center mb-[48px] md:text-[18px] leading-[20px] lg:leading-[22px] max-w-[880px] mx-auto font-normal text-textPrimary font-figtree"
    >
      A real person will be there to guide you through the entire setup. <br>
Most of our jewellers are fully onboarded and live on the platform with about  <br>
<span class="font-bold">2 hours of work, spread over a week.</span>
    </p>
     <button
      type="button"
      class="cursor-pointer bg-btnPrimary mx-auto text-white text-base leading-5 py-2 min-h-[56px]  min-w-[167px] px-6 rounded-full font-figtree font-medium flex items-center gap-3 btn-cta"
    >
          <Image src={btnIcon} class="w-5 h-5" alt="image" />

     Join Boutee
    </button>
  </div>
  </div>
</section>
